      "framework": "Top-Down Approach\nStart with total addressable population or market\nTop-Down Approach\nApply relevant filters: demographics, geography, income, eligibility\nTop-Down Approach\nEstimate penetration rate or adoption curve\nTop-Down Approach\nMultiply by average revenue per user/unit\nBottom-Up Approach\nCount existing providers/stores/units in the market\nBottom-Up Approach\nEstimate average revenue per provider/store/unit\nBottom-Up Approach\nCalculate total served market\nBottom-Up Approach\nCompare with top-down for cross-validation\nGrowth Projections\nHistorical growth rates and key drivers\nGrowth Projections\nSecular trends supporting or hindering growth\nGrowth Projections\nTechnology disruption potential\nGrowth Projections",
      "exhibit1": "Market data provided:\nKey insight: identify the most significant trend or gap in the data and explain its implications.\nAnalyze year-over-year trends to identify where performance is deteriorating\nCalculate the financial impact of each issue to prioritize\nCompare against industry benchmarks where available\n关键数据洞察：识别异常趋势是得分关键。好的面试者会立即指出\"哪个数字看起来不正常\"。\n趋势分析：对比各年度/季度数据，识别拐点和异常变化\n结构分析：计算各项目占总体的百分比，识别结构性变化\n竞争对标：与行业平均水平对比，判断是公司特有问题还是行业性问题\n根因假设：基于数据模式提出2-3个可能的根本原因，并逐一验证",
