      "framework": "Revenue Analysis\nRevenue trends: YOY growth rate, seasonal patterns, customer concentration\nRevenue Analysis\nPricing: average selling price trends, price vs volume decomposition\nRevenue Analysis\nCustomer mix: revenue by segment, channel, geography\nRevenue Analysis\nProduct mix: high-margin vs low-margin product revenue share\nCost Analysis\nVariable costs: COGS trends, input cost inflation, supplier dynamics\nCost Analysis\nFixed costs: SG&A, rent, depreciation, corporate overhead\nCost Analysis\nCost benchmarking: comparison with industry peers and best practices\nCost Analysis\nOperational efficiency: capacity utilization, labor productivity\nExternal Factors\nCompetitive dynamics: new entrants, pricing pressure, market share shifts\nExternal Factors\nRegulatory changes: new compliance requirements, tax changes\nExternal Factors\nMacroeconomic: inflation, interest rates, consumer spending trends\nExternal Factors",
